    (8,"Ni No Kuni: Wrath of the White Witch", 2011, 5, 4, 3, "https://www.mobygames.com/images/covers/l/723492-ni-no-kuni-wrath-of-the-white-witch-playstation-3-front-cover.jpg", 15.89, "PlayStation", "E-10", "Global", "Ni no Kuni: Wrath of the White Witch is a role-playing game that uses a third-person perspective. Players complete quests—linear scenarios with set objectives—to progress through the story."),
